articles.title: 'World's most dangerous bird': Video shows cassowary emerging from ocean off Australia coast - USA TODAY
articles.description: Video shows a bird considered by some to be the "world's most dangerous" emerging from the ocean off the coast of Australia on Oct. 31.
articles.content:
Beachgoers in Australia were shocked when an enormous bird, considered by some to be the world's most dangerous, emerged from the water on Oct. 31 and shook itself off.
